## Agent Routing

When the user references an agent by name, read the corresponding `.agent.md` file fully before responding. The agent's constraints and output format are binding for that session.

| User Says | Agent File | Primary Scope |
|-----------|-----------|---------------|
| `@engineer` | `.github/agents/engineer.agent.md` | Implementation, verification, delivery |
| `@architect` | `.github/agents/system-architect.agent.md` | System structure, API design, data model |
